title: Bratislava used a beer bell to end late-night drinking in public places
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Anna and Peter discover more spellbinding and unknown facts about Bratislava in this episode. Join them and you will learn why beer has long been considered liquid bread. 
 
Photo: TASR 
Book: Po stopách dávnej Bratislavy by V. Tomčík
